                "title": "雲來古劍法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">寒病鬼差</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/2575ddfaacc7015ebab2d17fba4593ea_905799654290741901.png",
                "key": "仙法．寒病鬼差",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "仙法．寒病鬼差"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">度厄真符</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">度厄真符</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色使用技能後：</span>如果該角色生命值未滿，則治療該角色2點。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/900dec327166a00218479cf8616072fc_2221304325487198022.png",
                "key": "仙法．救苦度厄",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "仙法．救苦度厄"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召喚物在場時，七七使用「普通攻擊」後：</span>治療受傷最多的我方角色1點。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6834059793264055678.png",
                "key": "寒病鬼差",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_5605580467179114571.png",
                "title": "寒病鬼差"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_9040948294929599123.png",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/21/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_4549435011443219144.png",
